metadata.name: l.1
metadata.description:
This little girl with a sudden resource for smile and play is coming from a high-strung past and an unrelenting future, like there is no escape . She took shape from the impalpable depths of an IPad exercise. This moment opened up a whole new territory for me after i was already a “master - mixer” of fine drawing and brush painting, with collage and photo manipulation.
Year of creation : 2014 - 2015
Part of the collection 
Cruel Fairy Tale / Chapter 3 / Taking-off
The artwork was exhibited at
2014 - AnnArt Gallery - Bucharest / Romania
2015 - ICR Lisbon - Portugal
2015 - Accademia di Romania - Roma / Italy 
2021 - Victoria Center - Bucharest / Romania
